
## Pet-Database Console-Based Application


## Description
This project is a very simple pet database management system that allows users to view, add and save pet information (name, age).
Unique ID associated with each pet. 


## Program features
- View all the pets in a clean formatted table.
- Add new pets to the database.
- Remove an existing pet
- Save the database to a txt file to write/read. 


## Usage
When you run the program, you will be presented with a menu:
1. View all pets
2. Add new pets
3. Remove an existing pet
4. Exit Program

## Acknowledgments
- The list of 5 pet names and ages was generated using AI.


